\f0\fs24 \cf0 The next time Annabel saw Anthony Tidkins was also the first time that Annabel had ever really been caught stealing. It was nothing overly fancy. A necklace. But the theft had been overly brazen, even for her; she\'92d stolen it right off a lady\'92s neck. 
\i \
