\i0 \cf0 She had nearly gotten away with it, too. The lady seemed not to have noticed the absence of her jewelry from her neck. She must not have felt Annabel\'92s little fingers unclasping the necklace while the lady shopped. It was the lady\'92s husband that caught her. A large, burly man who seized Annabel by the wrists and threatened to break her arms for her crime.
\i \
